Title: Watashi no Kamifuusen
Description: ['The original rendition of ', Watashi no Kamifuusen, ' sung by Akai Tori and animated by Mouri Atsushi. Due to the copyright law of the time, price of film reels, and overwriting tapes, ', Watashi no Kamifuusen, ' from 1971 remains to be one that is missing both its audio tape and video tape, as such the music video as a whole is considered lost media.']
